-- China Wants More Private Investment in Mining, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-02-09T15:26:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-09/china-wants-more-private-investment-in-mining-xinhua-reports.html
China wants to encourage more private
investment in the  mining industry  and will publicize information
on potential mining sites, Xinhua News Agency said today, citing
Minister of Land and Resources Xu Shaoshi.  The information system will give private investors “low-
risk access” to the industry, Xinhua reported, citing Xu.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
